      "id": "894908377039890",
      "score": 1,
      "review_title": "Developers, please fix this!",
      "review_description": "Why are you ruining your game with these updates? Halloween is long gone. You just brought the game back and said, \"Here, I brought you Lethal Ape 3 with a bunch of bugs and unfinished features, enjoy! Why are there so few people playing my game? I brought it back!\" I'll answer your question — I understand it's difficult to devote a lot of time to your games, but people want to play this game normally, without bugs. I'll list the things you need to fix, and I hope you'll fix your game: finally remove the Halloween update, HALLOWEEN IS LONG GONE! Second: add a Boombox player to the store so that instead of the store's background music, there is Boombox. It will be much more interesting, and you can take it with you and run away from monsters to the music of the Boombox player. Second: please fix the bugs with gus, red gus, and brown gus. They can see me in the backrooms from a kilometer away, and I don't even have time to get into the backrooms. Third: please add a swimming pool :( Fourth: please add hats and all kinds of clothes to the store. Fifth: this is very important to me... Add the old model of Gus when he was all black and had white eyes, and he played the song Wake Up The President, i love this! And lastly, sixth: remove the function in the mod menu that allows all monsters to teleport to the player, as this function can be used to remove all monsters from the textures. By the way, could you create a separate room in the lobby where there would be statues of all the monsters and their names? I think it would be really cool. Please remove RPG weapon? Developers, I'm not forcing you to make an update right away, and I can't even force you, I'm just asking you to DO IT. Then you will definitely have a lot of players. I'll add that some players who have mod menus scare me a lot. They can become invisible and make scary sounds. It makes my friends and me uncomfortable, and even some players don't like it. Please add quest-cam. That's all, please fix your game :(",
